### Snapshot tooling ###
# Local snapshot config (secrets) and generated bundles must never be committed.
deploy/snapshot/.env
deploy/snapshot/snapshots/

### Local data-clone workflow ###
# Local config (covered by *.env too) and downloaded bundles must never be committed.
deploy/local/.env
deploy/local/snapshots/
# Transient dump copied into deploy/ by the restore orchestrator.
deploy/deploy-local-restore-*.dump

